data.name: CreateDashboardStagingPriority35
ReadCsePersonAddressCsePersonCase
data.value: select distinct T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.SOURCE, T1.TYPE, T1.WORKER_ID, T1.VERIFIED_DATE, T1.END_DATE, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.LOCATION_TYPE, T2.TYPE, T3.NUMB, T3.STATUS, T3.STATUS_DATE, T3.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T3.INTERSTATE_CASE_ID, T3.NO_JURISDICTION_CD from CKT_CASE T3, CKT_CSE_PERSON T2 join CKT_CSE_PERS_ADDR T1 on (T1.VERIFIED_DATE between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) and T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP < @createdTimestamp and T2.NUMB = T1.CSP_NUMBER where exists ( select * from CKT_CASE_ROLE T4 where T2.NUMB = T4.CSP_NUMBER and T4.TYPE = 'AP' and (T1.VERIFIED_DATE between T4.START_DATE and T4.END_DATE) and T3.NUMB = T4.CAS_NUMBER ) order by T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, NCP_LOC_BY_ADRSS from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'CW'

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DATE, NCP_LOC_BY_ADRSS from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: ReadInfrastructure
data.value: select SYSTEM_GENERATED_I, EVENT_ID, REASON_CODE, CASE_NUMBER, CSE_PERSON_NUM, CREATED_BY, CREATED_TIMESTAMP, REFERENCE_DATE from CKT_INFRASTRUCTURE where EVENT_ID = 10 and CSE_PERSON_NUM = @csePersonNum and CASE_NUMBER = @caseNumber and (REASON_CODE in ('ADDROSKS', 'ADDRVRFDAP', 'FADDRVRFDAP')) and cast(@date1 as date) <= cast(CREATED_TIMESTAMP as date) and cast(@date2 as date) >= cast(CREATED_TIMESTAMP as date) and (REFERENCE_DATE between cast(@date1 as date) and cast(@date2 as date)) order by CREATED_TIMESTAMP desc

data.name: ReadServiceProviderOfficeServiceProvider
data.value: select T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID, T1.USER_ID, T2.OFF_GENERATED_ID, T2.ROLE_CODE, T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE from CKT_SERVICE_PRVDER T1 join CKT_OFFC_SRVC_PRVR T2 on T1.USER_ID = @userId and T1.SERVICE_PRVDER_ID = T2.SPD_GENERATED_ID and T2.ROLE_CODE = 'CO' and T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T2.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate order by T2.EFFECTIVE_DATE desc

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set NCP_LOC_BY_ADRSS = @ncpLocByAdrss where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI35 set AS_OF_DATE = @asOfDate, NCP_LOC_BY_ADRSS = @ncpLocByAdrss where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
